{"tid":2237581,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"16歲巨乳少女動手術縮胸","createTime":"2020-10-10T11:44:11.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-11T06:04:37.000Z","uid":25345,"like":0,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"8a96f1d88856cead5854bb3ced9d751c7e709fe2","tid":2237581,"uid":25345,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-10T11:44:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/juh2DhviCe_m7MpqX-rzhjOQlnY=/802x802/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/OPO7VOXPFBOFSJP3F4Y3R4LUBA.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2Fjuh2DhviCe_m7MpqX-rzhjOQlnY%3D%2F802x802%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FOPO7VOXPFBOFSJP3F4Y3R4LUBA.jpg&h=6a2dd221&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n海南省一名原來開朗的女孩，受巨乳症所累，性格變得孤僻，垂到肚臍的胸部亦讓瘦小的她舉步維艱。近日，她獲一間醫院免費治療，準備今日進行縮胸手術，並在手術前特別拍下這對巨乳<br />\n這名叫小薇的少女，16歲讀中二，去年7月發現乳房異常不斷脹大，她深怕家人發現而掩飾，故變得孤僻、敏感，更害怕見陌生人。去年底，她的姊姊無意發現她的乳房嚴重下垂，帶她到醫院檢查查不出病因。父母於是帶她四出求醫，上月29日，被確定是雌性激素分泌過多導致巨乳症"},{"pid":"165744eabd8bd3be25573b5ae3832240b79cc453","tid":2237581,"uid":42978,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-10T11:46:08.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"red\">2010.08.04</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/china/20100804/KEQWYNYWQOKK3IU5ZSKFXRWFRE/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20100804%2FKEQWYNYWQOKK3IU5ZSKFXRWFRE%2F&d=qh2qPVBUtyR5HqmPKg%2BIDHwIqWfEp03u%2FOlStsvMnxY%3D&h=918a9aa8\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20100804%2FKEQWYNYWQOKK3IU5ZSKFXRWFRE%2F&h=6bf2ba6f\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/china/20100804/KEQWYNYWQOKK3IU5ZSKFXRWFRE/</a>"},{"pid":"9fcbdcb04215ed7c4e4037426e24cbb9d65cc420","tid":2237581,"uid":42064,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-10T13